com.absio.database.table

Class Users

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.absio.database.table.AbstractTable
      • com.absio.database.table.Users

  • public class Users
extends AbstractTable
    This class represents the Users table. It has the logic for producing all relevant SQL for inserting, updating deleting and reading from the table.
